high_descs: move to the end table to the left of the bed
pick up a cd from the table
move to the dresser to the right of the bed
put the CD in a bowl on the dresser
pick up the bowl with the CD from the dresser
move to the end table to the left of the bed
put the bowl on the end table
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a CD on a end table.

high_descs: Turn around to your left walk towards the wall then turn right walk towards the side table
Pick up the cd on the edge of the  side table
Turn around to your right walk straight, turn left then left again head to the drawer
Put the cd in the bowl on the drawer
Pick up the bowl with cd on the drawer
Turn to your right walk straight then turn right, head to the side table
Put the bowl with cd on the side table
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with cd on the side table

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the nightstand.
Pick up the bottom cd.
Turn around and walk to the chair then turn left and walk to the dresser that's on the wall in front of you and face the left side of it so you're looking at a clear bowl.
Put the cd in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl.
Walk back to where you got the cd from.
Put the bowl on top of the cd.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a cd in it on the nightstand.
